// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0206 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a51b0301-f2c4-546c-9fd4-df6bf568d27b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
